# Gravité — Design Supremacy

Official website for Gravité, a strategic digital agency.  
Live demo: [https://fizarashid456.github.io/Gravite-Replica/](https://fizarashid456.github.io/Gravite-Replica/)

## About

Dark‑themed, responsive agency landing page.  
Built to showcase real work, real client testimonials, and actual contact details (no placeholders).  
Includes smooth scroll animations, glassmorphism navbar, and a floating coin hero.

## Features

- Fully responsive (mobile, tablet, desktop)
- Fixed glass‑style navbar with hamburger menu on mobile
- Scroll‑triggered fade‑up animations (Intersection Observer)
- Floating coin in hero section (CSS animation)
- Realistic insights section (no generic AI blog titles)
- Testimonial with actual CEO photo and name
- WhatsApp chat button + back to top button
- SVG icons, Google Fonts (Inter + Playfair Display)

## Tech 

- HTML5
- CSS3 (Grid, Flexbox, custom keyframes, media queries)
- Vanilla JavaScript (no frameworks)
- GitHub Pages for hosting

